{"lastModified":1768317604218,"uri":"c::18121026674::vessel::94c71fc0-da97-11f0-a801-250cd89c4cf2","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sardinia\n\nPershing 50.1. Motorboat rental in Sardinia Built by the renowned Pershing shipyard, the Pershing 50.1 It is a modern boat with sporty lines that exudes quality and solidity. On the outside, this motorboat features a generous cockpit with a large dining table and an L-shaped sofa, complemented by a spacious bow area with comfortable sun pads. Below deck, there are three ample cabins: forward, a stunning owner’s cabin with a king-size bed and private bathroom; in addition, there are two other spacious cabins and another bathroom with a shower. The layout is completed by a dinette with breathtaking space and a large galley opposite the dinette’s sofa, equipped with everything you need to prepare gourmet meals. This charter boat in Sardinia also offers a skipper’s cabin with its own bathroom and separate entrance, as well as a generator and air conditioning.","blueprint":{"name":"PERSHING 50.1","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::94c71fc0-da97-11f0-a801-250cd89c4cf2::assets::15f41ba0-da9f-11f0-bb7a-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::94c71fc0-da97-11f0-a801-250cd89c4cf2::assets::1624c890-da9f-11f0-bb7a-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::94c71fc0-da97-11f0-a801-250cd89c4cf2::assets::1621bb50-da9f-11f0-bb7a-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::94c71fc0-da97-11f0-a801-250cd89c4cf2::assets::15f55420-da9f-11f0-bb7a-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::94c71fc0-da97-11f0-a801-250cd89c4cf2::assets::15f2e320-da9f-11f0-bb7a-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::94c71fc0-da97-11f0-a801-250cd89c4cf2::assets::15f442b0-da9f-11f0-bb7a-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::94c71fc0-da97-11f0-a801-250cd89c4cf2::assets::15f35850-da9f-11f0-bb7a-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant